name: UnagiBox

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: unagi box
des: This skill can tell you the name of any episode of the popular TV series FRIENDS. All you have to do is ask for a particular episode by providing a season number and episode number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
